---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - K-Drama Kitchen">
  <article class="page-container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: January 15, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <section class="page-content">
      <p class="lead">
        Your privacy matters to us. This policy explains how K-Drama Kitchen collects,
        uses, and protects your information.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        K-Drama Kitchen is a static website that does not require user registration.
        We collect limited information through:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — Anonymous usage data via Google Analytics (pages visited, time spent, device type)</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies</strong> — Small files stored on your browser for analytics and advertising purposes</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To understand how visitors use our site</li>
        <li>To improve our content and user experience</li>
        <li>To serve relevant advertisements</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — For website traffic analysis. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — For displaying advertisements. Ads may be personalized based on your browsing history.</li>
        <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — For affiliate product links. See Affiliate Disclosure below.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        K-Drama Kitchen is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program,
        an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn
        advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
      </p>
      <p>
        This means that when you click on certain product links on our site and make a purchase,
        we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you. These commissions help
        support the operation of this website and allow us to continue creating content.
      </p>
      <p>
        We only recommend products that we believe will be helpful to our readers.
        Our opinions are our own and are not influenced by any affiliate relationships.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may
        affect some functionality of the site.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>To opt out of Google Analytics: <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out</a></li>
        <li>To manage ad preferences: <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
        personal information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
        with an updated revision date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this privacy policy? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:re171113@gmail.com">re171113@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .updated {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .page-content .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .page-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 40px 0 16px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .page-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .page-content ul {
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .page-content li {
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .page-content li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .page-content li strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .page-content a {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .page-content a:hover {
    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-container {
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    .page-content .lead {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
